When  Morgan Stanley (MS)  said in 
January it had cut its "net exposure" to Italy by $3.4 billion, 
it didn't tell investors that the nation paid that entire 
amount to the bank to exit a bet on  interest rates . (Source: 
Bloomberg)  Running Time: 02:02
 